readme:
This plugin adds a little link icon to every tab.

!! Settings

* Have a closer look at the "settings-tab" here or
* Open the ''$:/ControlPanel -> Settings -> WikiLabs'' tab

''Important:'' This plugin overrides the core `tabs-tab` macro defined in [[$:/core/macros/tabs]]

!! CSS Classes

The link icon `<span>` element uses the following classes:

|!Class |!Description |
|`wltc-link-to-tab` |Base class — always present |
|`wltc-is-shadow` |Tab tiddler is a shadow tiddler |

!! Customisation Examples

Add the CSS below to a stylesheet tiddler tagged `$:/tags/Stylesheet`.

!!! Hide icons in sidebar tabs

```css
.tc-sidebar-tabs .wltc-link-to-tab {
    display: none;
}
```

!!! Style shadow tiddler tab icons differently

```css
.wltc-is-shadow svg {
    color: <<colour muted-foreground>>;
    opacity: 0.5;
}
```

!!! Hide icons in tiddlers with a specific tag

Use the `data-tags` attribute on `.tc-tiddler-view-frame`:

```css
[data-tags*="MyTag"].tc-tiddler-view-frame .wltc-link-to-tab {
    display: none;
}
```

!!! Resize icons in tiddlers with a specific tag

```css
[data-tags*="MyTag"].tc-tiddler-view-frame .tc-tab-selected + .wltc-link-to-tab svg {
    width: 2.0em;
    height: 2.0em;
}
```
